{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7098bb6446","title":"右派言论——“任何独裁政治都要为民主潮流所冲垮”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"23167106d7","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"7098bb6446"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"8685694d5c","name":"曹文正"},{"id":"95cfcbd64c","name":"张继武"},{"id":"a7a2fdf6f7","name":"兰州大学"},{"id":"b22c389bab","name":"曹觉民"},{"id":"c712c62eff","name":"秦效斌"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"604a17cf5d","type":"title","text":"右派言论——“任何独裁政治都要为民主潮流所冲垮”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7098bb6446"},{"id":"96f60c29fd","type":"authors","text":"兰州大学曹觉民曹文正秦效斌张继武","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7098bb6446"},{"id":"0c44d8cd92","type":"paragraph","text":"“人类已经进步到使用原子能了，居然有人还想用奴隶主对待奴隶的方法对群众进行统治，我认为这是愚蠢的，也是不会成功的。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7098bb6446"},{"id":"10fc48839e","type":"paragraph","text":"任何形式的独裁政治和特务政治（指党的政策）都要为世界上汹涌澎湃的民主潮流所冲垮的。”（兰州大学　曹觉民）","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7098bb6446"},{"id":"2782780562","type":"paragraph","text":"“解放前有特务，解放后也有特务，那些专门作汇报工作的党团员就是属于这一种。”（兰州大学曹文正）","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7098bb6446"},{"id":"0e1fb6b858","type":"paragraph","text":"“不要跟他们走（指党、团员），跟他们走是特别危险，党员和团干部是“统治者”，党支部书记是陛下。”（兰州大学秦效斌）","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7098bb6446"},{"id":"f75ba8b942","type":"paragraph","text":"“学生党团员在分配宿舍中起着监视群众的作用，党团员是便衣警察。”（兰州大学　张继武）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7098bb6446"},{"id":"24c914ac7f","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《高等学校右派言论选编》（中共中国人民大学委员会，1958年8月）。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7098bb6446"}],"page":{"id":"bce4042b6a","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7098bb6446","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SS